channel.title: Comments on: Sub Pop opens virtual mom & pop

item.title: By: beatmaster23
item.dc:creator: beatmaster23
item.description: fantastic idea from subpop... however, at $9.90 a piece, it's a bit pricey, considering there are in theory no middlemen to pay and no packaging involved...
